name: Brain Zaps IV
description:
This piece is part of a series of mine (Chaotic Mind , 2022).

-

"The sudden pain in my head was unlike anything I'd ever felt. I felt like my brain was being zapped. I couldn't see or think straight, and the only thing I could focus on was the throbbing in my head."

-

Abstract light-painting created with steel wool on fire in pitch darkness. It was complemented by digital art.

*

'Brain Zaps IV', 2022
